sequenceDiagram
    participant Orchestrator as FMS Guardrails<br/>Orchestrator
    participant Detector as Regex Detector<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

    Note over Orchestrator,Detector: Flow 1: Text Content Detection

    Orchestrator->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP<br/>No Auth, No TLS (platform-level)
    Note right of Detector: Request body:<br/>{ contents: [string],<br/>  detector_params: {<br/>    regex: [pattern_names<br/>    or custom regex] } }

    alt Built-in Pattern (e.g. "email", "ssn", "credit_card")
        Note right of Detector: Lookup in pattern registry<br/>HashMap<&str, fn><br/>Pre-compiled detector function
    else Custom Regex Pattern
        Note right of Detector: Compile regex at request time<br/>via Regex::new()<br/>(no cross-request caching)
    end

    Note right of Detector: Execute regex matching<br/>against each content string<br/>(linear-time guarantee)

    Detector-->>Orchestrator: HTTP 200 JSON Response<br/>{ detections: [{ start, end,<br/>  text, detection, score,<br/>  detection_type }] }

    Note over Orchestrator,Detector: Flow 2: Health Check

    Orchestrator->>Detector: GET /health<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP
    Detector-->>Orchestrator: HTTP 200 "healthy"
